<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>This function allows you to correct and merge separated and overlapping surfaces with a single click.</p><p><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Features</h2><p>By simply indicating the 3D model, the software automatically searches for overlapping surfaces, surface separation, and missing surfaces, and corrects and combines them.<br>The result is a significant reduction in man-hours.<br><br></p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/A40C6052-9FA0-3046-A1FF-A16F1F90CC31.jpeg" alt="" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3>&nbsp;</h3><h3 class="fr-text-bordered">Inquiries</h3><p>If you have any inquiries about our product or would like to request a visit to your place for explanation or demonstration, please use the inquiry form.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://uelthai.co.th/contact"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Contact Us &rarr;</span></a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p